    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"> <p>Welcome to The Frick Collection and the Frick Art Reference Library. Please follow the links at the left for more specific information about hours, admission policies, audiovisual information, accessibility, contact information, and general information about both The Frick Collection and the Frick Art Reference Library.</p>
<p><a href="//www.frick.org/../../visit/museum">The Frick Collection </a></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">1 East 70th Street<br />
  New York, NY 10021<br />
  Phone: 212-288-0700</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">General e-mail: <a href="mailto:info@frick.org">info@frick.org</a></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">For general information about visiting, see <a href="//www.frick.org/../../visit/museum">Collection</a>.</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">For entry fees, see <a href="//www.frick.org/visit/museum/admission">Admission</a> and see <a href="//www.frick.org/visit/museum/hours">Hours and Holidays</a> for opening times.</p>
<p><a href="//www.frick.org/research/library">Frick Art Reference Library</a></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">10 East 71st Street<br />
  New York, NY 10021<br />
  Phone: 212-547-0641</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">General e-mail: <a href="mailto:library@frick.org">library@frick.org</a></p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">If asking a research question, see <a href="//www.frick.org/research/library/ask-question" target="_blank">Ask a Question</a>.</p>
<p style="margin-left: 40px; ">For general information about visiting, see <a href="//www.frick.org/visit/library">Visit &gt; Library.</a></p>
